snippet.title: Dreamcast Paranoia - ParanoiaDC Beta 1
snippet.description:
The goldsource mod Paranoia being ported to Sega Dreamcast.

The first few maps from the industry map set from the first public beta.

Paranoia mod by Paranoia Dev Team, Dreamcast port by OVERRiDE and DREAMMATRiX.
